{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/study-blog/javascript-hoisting/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h1>변수 생성 단계</h1>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>단계</th>\n<th>설명</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>선언 단계(Declaration phase)</td>\n<td>변수 객체에 변수 등록<br/>변수 객체는 스코프가 참조하는 대상이 됨</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>초기화 단계(Initialization phase)</td>\n<td>변수 객체에 등록된 변수를 메모리에 할당<br/>변수를 undefined로 초기화</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>할당 단계(Assignment phase)</td>\n<td>undefined로 초기화된 변수에 실제값 할당</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h1>변수 호이스팅(Variable Hoisting)</h1>\n<p>모든 선언문(var, let, const, function, function*, class)이 코드의 선두로 끌어 올려진 것처럼 동작하는 특징</p>\n<p>선언되기 이전에 참조 가능</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>var</p>\n<p>선언과 초기화가 한번에 이루어짐 → 선언문 이전에 변수에 접근해도 에러 X</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/84bb7f3a80532cc2c190d4dce5f60c11/e26aa/var-lifecycle.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 22.395833333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/84bb7f3a80532cc2c190d4dce5f60c11/a59e9/var-lifecycle.webp 192w,\n/static/84bb7f3a80532cc2c190d4dce5f60c11/0ca9f/var-lifecycle.webp 384w,\n/static/84bb7f3a80532cc2c190d4dce5f60c11/dc9b9/var-lifecycle.webp 768w,\n/static/84bb7f3a80532cc2c190d4dce5f60c11/de60b/var-lifecycle.webp 1016w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/84bb7f3a80532cc2c190d4dce5f60c11/3b721/var-lifecycle.png 192w,\n/static/84bb7f3a80532cc2c190d4dce5f60c11/66595/var-lifecycle.png 384w,\n/static/84bb7f3a80532cc2c190d4dce5f60c11/fe486/var-lifecycle.png 768w,\n/static/84bb7f3a80532cc2c190d4dce5f60c11/e26aa/var-lifecycle.png 1016w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/84bb7f3a80532cc2c190d4dce5f60c11/fe486/var-lifecycle.png\"\n            alt=\"post\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 스코프의 선두에서 선언 단계와 초기화 단계가 실행</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 따라서 변수 선언문 이전에 변수 참조 가능</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// undefined</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> foo\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// undefined</span>\n\nfoo <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 할당문에서 할당 단계가 실행</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 1</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>let</p>\n<p>선언과 초기화가 분리되어 진행</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6f56a2eac7ea3a642280864ba522780c/1d15d/let-lifecycle.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 35.9375%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/6f56a2eac7ea3a642280864ba522780c/a59e9/let-lifecycle.webp 192w,\n/static/6f56a2eac7ea3a642280864ba522780c/0ca9f/let-lifecycle.webp 384w,\n/static/6f56a2eac7ea3a642280864ba522780c/dc9b9/let-lifecycle.webp 768w,\n/static/6f56a2eac7ea3a642280864ba522780c/ee9cc/let-lifecycle.webp 931w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/6f56a2eac7ea3a642280864ba522780c/3b721/let-lifecycle.png 192w,\n/static/6f56a2eac7ea3a642280864ba522780c/66595/let-lifecycle.png 384w,\n/static/6f56a2eac7ea3a642280864ba522780c/fe486/let-lifecycle.png 768w,\n/static/6f56a2eac7ea3a642280864ba522780c/1d15d/let-lifecycle.png 931w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/6f56a2eac7ea3a642280864ba522780c/fe486/let-lifecycle.png\"\n            alt=\"let-lifecycle\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 스코프의 선두에서 선언 단계가 실행</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 아직 변수가 초기화(메모리 공간 확보와 undefined로 초기화)되지 않음</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 따라서 변수 선언문 이전에 변수를 참조할 수 없음</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// ReferenceError: foo is not defined</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> foo <span class=\"token comment\">// 변수 선언문에서 초기화 단계가 실행</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// undefined</span>\n\nfoo <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 할당문에서 할당 단계가 실행</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 1</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>ES6에서는 호이스팅이 발생하지 않는 것처럼 보이지만, 코드 블록 내에서 선언해보면 호이스팅이 발생하는 것을 확인할 수 있음</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> foo <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 전역 변수</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// ReferenceError: foo is not defined</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> foo <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 지역 변수</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>let은 블록 레벨 스코프이기 때문에 전역 변수의 값이 출력되지 않음</p>\n<p>지역 변수가 해당 스코프에서 호이스팅되어 TDZ에 빠지게 되고 참조 에러 발생</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>참고</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://poiemaweb.com/js-data-type-variable\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">PoiemaWeb</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"page":"study-blog","categories":["JavaScript"],"date":"Invalid date","title":"변수 생성 단계 및 호이스팅(Variable Hoisting)","subTitle":null}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/study-blog/javascript-hoisting/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}